## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- Open each screen.
- Attempt to submit the form without entering data.
- Verify that error messages appear ("This field is required" or similar).
- Enter invalid data (where applicable) and verify validation.
- Enter valid data and verify submission proceeds.
